title: Joko & Klaas gegen ProSieben
overview: Their new opponent is big, red and more powerful than ever: Now Joko and Klaas are not competing against each other for the first time, but instead challenge an entire broadcaster. The goal is to compete against the entire universe of the red seven. Moderators, editors, entire programs - Joko and Klaas invite everyone to the cross-program strength test in various game rounds.
